[SN]TITLE[SN]
'Severe delays' on M4 at Newport after four-car crash

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
There are "severe" delays on the M4 westbound near Newport after a four-car crash.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Authorities said two lanes had been closed on Wednesday after the incident between junction 27 (High Cross) and junction 28 (Tredegar Park).
Both have since reopened but there is congestion to junction 24 (Coldra).
